explanations.description: Various proper nouns, including geographical locations (e.g., Canada, Sochi, Russia, Iowa, Edmonton, Saskatchewan), names of people (e.g., Thad Matta, Greg Westlake, Corbin Watson, Tessa Virtue, Scott Mo), team names (e.g., Continental Cup, Wheat Kings, Team North America), and event names (e.g., Olympics, Paralympics, Paralympic Games, WTA Championships), as well as some common nouns related to sports and games (e.g., curling, hockey, softball).
